  🏛️  Per-Organization API (standardized contract):
     Replace {org} with: university, government, employer, hospital, financial

     GET  /orgs/{org}/api/v1/health                    — Org health
     GET  /orgs/{org}/api/v1/organizations/profile     — Org profile
     GET  /orgs/{org}/api/v1/entities/search           — Search entities
     GET  /orgs/{org}/api/v1/entities/:id              — Entity detail
     GET  /orgs/{org}/api/v1/credentials               — List credentials
     POST /orgs/{org}/api/v1/credentials/issue         — Issue credential
     POST /orgs/{org}/api/v1/credentials/:id/revoke    — Revoke credential
     POST /orgs/{org}/api/v1/webhooks/events           — Send webhook event
     GET  /orgs/{org}/api/v1/events                    — Event log

  🔐 Authentication:
     Platform: X-API-Key: platform-admin-key
     Per-Org:  Use each org's individual API key shown above

